arStrings.szText: "Why didn't you just tell us we needed Ah Bulan's help from the start?"
Had you sought Ah Bulan before going to Neyrelle, you would have returned to find her dead, or worse: puppeted by her enemy.
She was fading, even then. For days she has battled Mephistoâ€™s influence. But the sight of you, the reminder that she is not alone, was more powerful than any potion.
By being there, in that moment, you helped her more than you could ever know.
